    {
        "content": "<p>The syntax is either <code>Quot.ind (β := fun m =&gt; predQ (succQ m) = m)</code> if you just want to specify <code>β</code> or <code>@Quot.ind _ _ (fun m =&gt; predQ (succQ m) = m)</code> if you want to make all the parameters explicit (the <code>_</code> placeholders are then for the two previous argument which should be found by unification).</p>",
